show.title: The World in my grasp
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा 
https://links.kukufm.com/wc2cq7
show.description: To marry his girlfriend, Finn Cooper toils as a laborer, enduring long days and surviving on instant noodles to save money, all while facing the scorn of those around him. Deeply troubled by his circumstances, he wishes for strength beyond his current limits. To his astonishment, his wish is granted, but in an unexpected twist. Everyone else becomes as fragile as water, making him the strongest man alive on the planet.
